1 jurisdiction. If the court finds that a violation occurred, the court may grant damages, civil
2 penalties, injunctive relief, attorney's fees, and any such other relief the court finds appropriate.
3 Notwithstanding section 407.100 to the contrary, civil penalties shall be as follows:
4 (1) Ten thousand dollars for the first violation; or
5 (2) Twenty thousand dollars for any subsequent violation."; and
6
